premise_source_doc_sentence: He appears in George Mihalka 's My Bloody Valentine and Patrick Lussier 's My Bloody Valentine 3D as one of the main antagonists .
After My Bloody Valentine 's debut mini album , This is Your Bloody Valentine  (  1985  )  , failed to receive much attention , the band relocated to London , United Kingdom .
My Bloody Valentine first experienced chart success with their EP The New Record by My Bloody Valentine  (  1986  )  , which entered the UK Independent Singles Chart at number 22 .
My Bloody Valentine formed in early 1983 and released their debut mini album , This Is Your Bloody Valentine , in January 1985 on Tycoon Records .
My Bloody Valentine , an alternative rock band from Dublin , Ireland , have recorded songs for three studio albums and a number of extended plays , singles and compilation releases .
